{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2bb573165f","title":"赵瑜的右派言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"07baa61fd7","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"2bb573165f"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4c0546f58a","name":"成都工学院"},{"id":"b2e69c5798","name":"赵瑜"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4058d38d26","type":"title","text":"赵瑜的右派言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"75e29a02ad","type":"authors","text":"成都工学院赵瑜","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"c2f2e13c7d","type":"subtitle","text":"(赵瑜：成都工学院教师)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"64d89c4729","type":"paragraph","text":"“三反搞得过火了，光整群众不整党员，整了像张洪沅这样大的知识分子，整得伤心，整得人抬不起头，不该斗，‘士可杀不可辱’。”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"1c9348e480","type":"paragraph","text":"肃反运动的偏差，“捉到了多少反革命？少！少！少！冤枉了多少好人？多！多！多！那些昧良心打击别人提高自己认为积极的人(意指肃反运动中的积极分子)，都是有黑心没良心”，“肃反整得太伤心了，整得别人抬不起头来”，他爱人就是肃反整伤心了整瘦了的。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"c60b5ad5b7","type":"paragraph","text":"“党员是残酷无情的黑心肠，没有良心的家伙。”","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"d742727ae5","type":"paragraph","text":"认为党变质了，“入党等于工作积极加上冷酷。”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"e0705c4737","type":"paragraph","text":"“党团员是人面兽心，冷酷无情，最卑鄙无耻的家伙。”","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"6d84bcd269","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党比帝国主义还残酷，共产党的心比帝国主义还狠，我把共产党恨透了，共青团是三青团。”","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"1f04cba434","type":"paragraph","text":"“共产党变质了，我极赞同葛佩奇说的：‘人民对共产党是在敬鬼神而远之。’”","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"505172968d","type":"paragraph","text":"“如果这次共产党不整风，恐怕中国也会发生匈牙利事件。”","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"9656f9cbeb","type":"paragraph","text":"“最近要求进步的人都是些‘捧党团员的屁股，抬党团员的轿子，捧上压下，拍马屁最卑鄙无耻最不要脸的人’。这些人是为了领‘橡皮饭碗’。”","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"015e4fd59b","type":"paragraph","text":"“林希翎讲的问题很有道理，应该请到学校来讲演。”","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"0aa7da78a5","type":"paragraph","text":"“现在说不会报复，最怕是一股风，这一股风过去了，就要遭整，要等两年后共产党彻底改变了，我才说。”","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"21387e1923","type":"paragraph","text":"“反右斗争就是扣大帽子，我根本就有抵触。”","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"1158eb2e54","type":"paragraph","text":"“现在收了，不要放了，谨防遭反。”","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"8477dcc9a1","type":"paragraph","text":"“如果反到我们头上来的话，我们也不怕，大家(指被他影响的那些人)都要去顶到不要溜边边。”","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"528a91497e","type":"paragraph","text":"“章罗解放前很进步，还被国民党逮捕坐过牢，章乃器是七君子之一，现在却给他们扣上右派帽子。”","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"44a5021319","type":"paragraph","text":"“这次(指反右斗争)总要反出几个积极分子来。”","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"df173a756f","type":"paragraph","text":"“反右是‘小题大作’，辩论会是斗争会，是整人。”","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"},{"id":"a57280bebc","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《右派言论选集》（中共成都工学院委员会办公室，1957年）。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f"}],"page":{"id":"d7b7caa526","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2bb573165f","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}